Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.98,0:00:14.45,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな　まさか…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it can not be...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.75,0:00:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you kill Mr. Earl ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.77,0:00:18.18,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,伯爵様を殺したのはお前か
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.88,0:00:21.70,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,バルカシオン伯爵は自ら命を絶たれた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.89,0:00:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Count Barkasion committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.86,0:00:22.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,うそだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.26,0:00:30.65,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は私を欺き続けたばかりか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.30,0:00:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only do you constantly deceived me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.88,0:00:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,also took away a loved one!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.90,0:00:32.84,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,大切な人までも奪った
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.71,0:00:36.06,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対に許さない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.73,0:00:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.47,0:00:47.30,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.91,0:00:51.64,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ルシタニアに女の兵士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.93,0:00:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Female soldier Lyusitanii?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.63,0:00:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay! Do not kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.68,0:00:52.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,待て　殺すな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.93,0:00:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There is!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.03,0:00:53.67,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.95,0:00:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Start up the Gentiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.02,0:00:55.64,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,放せ　異教徒ども
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.19,0:00:59.23,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,放せ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.20,0:00:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.59,0:01:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter XXV
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.09,0:01:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Battle for the Holy Emmanuel castle over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:14.76,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,聖マヌエル城を巡る戦いは終わった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Barkasion graph suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.72,0:01:19.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,城主バルカシオン伯は自害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.38,0:01:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Many of the followers of the faith Yaldabaoth too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.47,0:01:22.64,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,イアルダボート神に敬虔な者の多くも後に続き
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.52,0:01:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving only the sick and wounded,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.56,0:01:27.88,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,僅かに残った傷病者のみがパルス軍に救出された
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Salvation Army Parsis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.19,0:01:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Such is the will of the Crown Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.23,0:01:30.12,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,王太子殿下の御意である
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.41,0:01:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,To release those who have surrendered!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:33.92,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,降伏する者は助けよ　武器なき者は殺すな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.29,0:01:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not kill unarmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.92,0:01:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Darjun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.98,0:01:38.96,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.26,0:01:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Darjun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.26,0:01:41.92,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.55,0:01:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.56,0:01:46.54,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.03,0:01:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Darjun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:48.86,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.12,0:01:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.16,0:01:53.02,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫か
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.36,0:01:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince, I am ashamed to say it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.51,0:01:57.12,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下…　面目ございませぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.00,0:02:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but I was not able to do away with the silver mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.06,0:02:01.16,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あの銀仮面　討ち損じてしまいました
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.31,0:02:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.31,0:02:02.11,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,かまわぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.51,0:02:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The main thing is that you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.58,0:02:04.28,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お主が無事なら　それでよい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.11,0:02:06.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下も
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And you, Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.21,0:02:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:06.92,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.83,0:02:08.60,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,終わったぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.44,0:02:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We took the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.46,0:02:10.95,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,マヌエル城は落とした
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Under your command, we emerged victorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.58,0:02:22.30,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下の指揮の下　我々は勝ったのですね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.68,0:02:25.90,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　ありがとう　ダリューン
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.75,0:02:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank Daryun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:31.55,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,気を抜くな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.82,0:02:33.55,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,全室くまなく捜索しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.86,0:02:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Searched every room!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.70,0:02:34.38,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.74,0:02:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,While that success, you might say.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.12,0:02:37.58,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ひとまずは…　といったところか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.37,0:02:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,survivors lyusitaniantsev
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:42.63,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ルシタニアの生存者　僅かですが　拘束したそうです
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.77,0:02:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,a little, but they were taken into custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Put in a prison bunk and treat their wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:46.42,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,牢に寝床を作り　負傷者を治療してやってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:47.31,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.12,0:02:48.72,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.84,0:02:49.64,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What is about the unit, stormed the gates?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:52.18,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,突入部隊の消息は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.84,0:02:54.67,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それが…　まだ誰も
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.91,0:02:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So far ... no one was found.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.95,0:02:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:57.47,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか…　ご苦労
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:02:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.68,0:03:14.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アルフリード
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Alfrid ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.14,0:03:17.36,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あ…あれ　ナルサス
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,TO? Narsus ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.79,0:03:19.86,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,っていうか　私　どうなったの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, what happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I live?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:21.11,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,生きてる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I live!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:22.86,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,生きてる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:24.98,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.50,0:03:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. I am glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.55,0:03:27.86,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いや…　よかった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.62,0:03:36.42,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,少しは心配した？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a little worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:37.36,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.53,0:03:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman from the clan Zot's so easy to die, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.06,0:03:41.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ゾット族の女がそうやすやすと死ぬはずなかろうに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:44.90,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ　夫より先立つわけにはいかないしね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I can not die, and to throw her husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not remember that I became your husband ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.50,0:03:48.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,夫であると認めた覚えはないが…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:50.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,よっと　何ここ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.57,0:03:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Warehouse products.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:51.70,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,食料庫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:56.11,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,どうやら食物の搬入口に落ちて　気絶していたようだな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.05,0:03:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like you fell unconscious wherever they send food.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:57.64,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:03:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's how ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:03:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And what are you doing here, Narsus?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.99,0:04:00.04,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,でも　ナルサスはどうしてここに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:04.60,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私は最初から糧食の奪取を最優先に考えている
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,From the beginning I thought the replenishment provisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're from a good family, and worried about the food?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.98,0:04:07.96,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いい家の出なのに　食べ物にこだわるんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Even without a weapon, you can fight with your bare hands and mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:11.67,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,武器がなくても　知恵と素手で戦える
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.34,0:04:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But without food can not go far.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:15.35,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,だが食料がなくては　どうにもならないだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:20.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,軍師ってのは　いろいろ考えなきゃいけないんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the strategist needs to think about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.93,0:04:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Simple, Jaswant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:23.91,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,すまんな　ジャスワント
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:25.35,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,子細ない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.47,0:04:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:28.46,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン卿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Daryun, I am glad you are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:30.84,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたが無事でよかった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.82,0:04:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely, prince of the same opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:33.52,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下も　ひと安心のはず
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Prince became stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.88,0:04:36.42,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　殿下はたくましくなられた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He himself can handle, if required.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:39.11,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,もうお一人でも進んでいける
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:46.76,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それにしても　あなたほどの人にこんな手傷を負わせるとは
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,To someone so seriously hurt you ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.86,0:04:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Silver mask should not be underestimated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:50.70,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,その銀仮面の男　侮れませんね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.36,0:04:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,His fathomless darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:55.27,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツの闇は計り知れぬ　不気味な男だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.96,0:04:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange and terrible man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:05:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear the word fear from the knight in black.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.62,0:05:00.23,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,かの黒衣の騎士が随分と弱気なことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kisvard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:01.62,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,キシュワード殿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was not a whim that bastard, I would've been dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:05.99,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツの気まぐれがなければ　俺は討たれていた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.14,0:05:10.47,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜヤツは　とどめを刺していかなかったのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did not he dealt the final blow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed to me that he plays us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.15,0:05:13.24,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,弄んでいるつもりなのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He does not want to win, when the benefit is small.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:16.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,辛勝はヤツの望むところではないようだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:19.04,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,こしゃくなヤツめ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.87,0:05:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the same jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.39,0:05:20.51,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,おいおい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.53,0:05:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.49,0:05:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:21.71,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,もう大丈夫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,These wounds trifle in comparison with the Prince feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:25.32,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな傷　殿下のお気持ちを思えばなんともない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:37.04,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　ひと仕事終わったあとのフカーはうまい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.05,0:05:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,After a bit of work becomes more delicious wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were Marzbanom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:41.04,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お主　マルズバーンであったか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.74,0:05:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:42.83,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,一応な
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:44.40,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even among Marzbanov there are different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:48.19,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,マルズバーンにもさまざまなお人がいるものじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:51.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ　もう一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, even by the glass!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:52.62,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,頂こう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:02.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ここはよい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:02.90,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:08.04,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.35,0:06:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You!..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:11.42,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,一人だけこんな所にしてしまって　すまない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I put you here alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you have such a temper ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:13.84,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お主が暴れるからだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's true that the Count has committed suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:19.32,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,伯爵様が自害したのは本当なのだな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just like talking servants.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:21.83,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,従者たちの言ったとおりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Barkasion Earl was a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:31.06,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,バルカシオン伯爵様は立派な方だった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was he who put an end to the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.86,0:06:35.67,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　彼がこの戦いを終わらせた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:40.99,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,本来　戦いなど向いてない　お優しい方なのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, he was a good man, is not made for war.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.97,0:06:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in Peshavarde I met the real you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:48.46,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ペシャワールで出会ったのが本当の君だったのだな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:49.47,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,違う
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Etoile I, knight serving Barkasionu Count!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:53.47,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私はバルカシオン伯爵に仕える騎士　エトワールだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.96,0:06:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:58.30,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,おなか　すいているだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Here stew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:00.11,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,シチューを持ってきたから
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:02.96,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なっ　異教徒の施しなど受けられるか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never accept charity from the heathen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:05.96,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,もともとここにあった君たちのものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still your food.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:06.86,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,うるさい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.02,0:07:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you think otherwise?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:12.48,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,こう考えたらどうだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,For you this - the food of the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:15.50,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,これは君にとって敵の食べ物だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you eat it, reduce the enemy's reserves,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:19.90,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なら　これを君が食べれば敵の食料が減り
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.03,0:07:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and it will affect his army.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.03,0:07:22.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,敵に損害を与えることになる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is not it a wonderful goal in the battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:24.63,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,これは立派な武勲じゃないかな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:27.84,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ばかばかしい　そんな詭弁に誰が…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense! Who will lead to such a trick ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:28.60,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But, at least,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.16,0:07:32.72,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,だが少なくとも我が軍にとって　いいことはないのは本当だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,it will not benefit my army.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.99,0:07:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And it is true. These products are not your prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:38.39,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに　お前たちの得にはならないな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:41.40,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,パンもどうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And the bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you tell your story?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:48.52,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,よければ聞かせてくれないか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you decide to become a knight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.52,0:07:51.54,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ君は騎士になろうと思ったのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My real name is Estelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:08:02.86,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私の本名はエステルというが　その名は捨てた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I tossed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.16,0:08:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:03.88,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.22,0:08:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Estelle - a girl's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:05.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,エステルとは女の名だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:10.71,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私は騎士の家に養子としてもらわれた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I was adopted by a knight family,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,who had no heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.50,0:08:13.72,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,その家には跡継ぎがいなくてな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So I decided that I should become a knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:17.39,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,だから　私が騎士となると決めたのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.71,0:08:19.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それで男になろうと…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And become a man ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! No problems will be, if I'm a guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:22.67,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ　私が男なら　なんの問題もない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.43,0:08:31.11,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,思い出すな　あのときのことは忘れろ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough to remember! Forget about that meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:32.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いいな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Clear. Pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:35.38,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか　残念だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:36.28,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:37.43,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　いや…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:42.44,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,もう少しお前たちの食料を減らしてやりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a little more to reduce your stocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A supplement?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:44.03,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,おかわりだね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:45.96,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,他のものなら　あるから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.72,0:08:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:55.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,パルスのアルスラーン王子というヤツは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that Prince Arslan on his head has two curved horns.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:59.17,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,２本のねじ曲がった角が生えていると聞いていた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:04.28,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,よもや貴様のような坊ちゃんだったとはな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And I could not think that you're just a spoiled kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.74,0:09:07.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,大人になったら　角が生えてくるかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,When he grew up, they can grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.12,0:09:11.98,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,変わっているな　お前は
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a strange guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.18,0:09:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I sometimes say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:16.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,時々そう言われる　自分ではよく分からないが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Although he did not notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:21.06,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,王が王らしくせぬから　パルスは都を奪われる目に遭うのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The king did not fulfill his duty,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Parsa here and lost his capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:23.32,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,王らしく…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.11,0:09:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Their duty ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:24.58,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なあ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Say ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:28.56,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,このような戦を避ける方法はないのだろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a way to avoid this war?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:31.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,無理な話だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you do not stop pochetat all the idols and false gods
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:37.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お前たちが偶像や邪神を敬うのをやめ　真の神を崇めぬかぎり
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and refuse to accept the faith of the true God, we will always fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:39.12,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,我らは戦い続ける
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:44.12,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,だから　異教徒は皆殺しにしてもよい…か
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to destroy the Gentiles?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:45.58,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.18,0:09:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can not agree with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:49.02,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私にはとてもそう思えない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.18,0:09:49.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだと
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let our philosophy and different,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:54.54,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,考え方が違っても　共に暮らすやり方もあるのではないだろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Can not we find a way to live together?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:56.30,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなものあるはずない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.66,0:09:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It is simply impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.22,0:10:00.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それは…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It!..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:04.06,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,君から受け取ったこれを　今日まで何度も読んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You gave me this, and I re-read many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:08.84,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,これは君たちにとっては　すばらしい教えだと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that you are the best teachings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:10.32,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,でも
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But those who are now in power in Lyusitanii ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:12.90,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,今のルシタニアの権力者たちは
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.24,0:10:15.70,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,この教えを利用しているだけなのではないか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.35,0:10:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,probably just use this teaching for their own purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.81,0:10:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what are you? ..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:17.63,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,な…何を
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of their own greed and ambition
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:19.73,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,自分たちの欲望と野心のために
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They hide behind the name of God
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.06,0:10:23.14,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,神の名を利用して　君たちに殺戮をさせている
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and pushing you to kill others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes no sense to kill others because they are pagans!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:26.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,異教徒だからといって　殺す必要はない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.12,0:10:28.93,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,黙れ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, shut up ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:30.46,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,黙れ　黙れ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.95,0:10:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:32.51,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜそんなことを言うんだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out! Nothing do not want to hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:35.89,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,出ていけ　お前と話すことはない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.56,0:10:42.33,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ごめんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not want to teach or judge you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.11,0:10:45.39,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,偉そうに君を責めるつもりはなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Etoile.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.39,0:10:53.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,エトワール
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You can read the prayer of faith Yaldabaoth?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:57.35,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,君はイアルダボート教の祈りの言葉を唱えられるか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.14,0:10:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.23,0:10:59.12,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,当たり前だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then pray for the dead tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.83,0:11:03.04,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,だったら明日　死者に祈りをささげてくれないか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.48,0:11:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Lyusitaniantsam dead need their prayers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.55,0:11:07.91,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ルシタニアの死者にはルシタニアの祈りが必要だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:16.18,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私は…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.00,0:11:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Spoiled ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:22.25,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あの坊ちゃん…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He specifically?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:24.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,わざとか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.51,0:12:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.52,0:12:01.24,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This soldier Lyusitanii.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:03.23,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ルシタニアの兵士じゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.26,0:12:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.26,0:12:13.35,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,生きていたか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.81,0:12:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Comrades who fought with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:29.56,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,共に戦った同胞たちよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Followers of the faith Yaldabaoth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:34.09,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,イアルダボートの聖なる信徒たちよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Be blessed on God's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:39.15,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,汝らは神のもとに祝福される
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:43.39,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,魂よ　安らかなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Soul Rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:53.46,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,聖マヌエル城は陥落
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy Emmanuel Castle fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.82,0:12:57.66,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,城主バルカシオン伯以下　城内の者はほとんど戦死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Count Barkasion and most died in combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:12:59.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アルスラーン率いるパルス軍は
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:13:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They say the army, led by Arslan,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.95,0:13:03.58,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,近日中にも　エクバターナに向けて出立するものと思われます
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.14,0:13:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,on any given day can go to Ecbatana.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.61,0:13:06.28,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんということだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How is this possible ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.63,0:13:11.10,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,魂よ　安らかなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,People pokoytesy with mirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.72,0:13:16.13,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,銀仮面はどうした　大きな口をたたきおって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.83,0:13:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the silver mask ?! This because we are pushing here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:17.02,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それが…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:18.47,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ここにいる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.02,0:13:26.72,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様　よくもおめおめと帰還できたものだな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You! As you have enough nerve to come back so shamelessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:33.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,{\fsp0\fs53}聖マヌエル城とやらはイアルダボート神のご加護に恵まれなかったのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Castle of Emmanuel
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not deserve the blessings Yaldabaoth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:36.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,軽々しく神の御名を口にするな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.55,0:13:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not speak so lightly of the Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you going to compensate for his failure ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.53,0:13:39.38,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,此度の失態　どう償うつもりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.55,0:13:41.69,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,失態？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Failure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.08,0:13:46.64,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,何がおかしい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.19,0:13:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:50.75,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,こやつをひっ捕らえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Seize him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You are crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:03.16,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,血迷ったか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.50,0:14:06.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,人払いをしてやったまでだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.63,0:14:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so we can talk in private.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:09.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,我が名はヒルメス
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Hermes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.40,0:14:12.55,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,父の名はオスロエスという
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.51,0:14:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My father - Osroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.07,0:14:16.06,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,パルスの先王　オスロエス
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The former king of Parsa, Osroes ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:19.56,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,父を殺した簒奪者アンドラゴラスと
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.42,0:14:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Andragoras usurper who killed my father,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:22.99,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,その小せがれに思い知らせる必要がある
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and his son had to realize,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.51,0:14:25.58,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,パルスの正統な王は
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.61,0:14:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that the true king of Parsa am I, Hermes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.81,0:14:29.51,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,この俺　ヒルメスだということをな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:32.71,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:35.89,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はなから我が国を利用するために…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You from the beginning using my country ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.55,0:14:39.12,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ素性を明かす気になった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why suddenly I decided to reveal himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.99,0:14:42.55,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の真に望むものはなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you wish really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.62,0:14:45.11,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,パルスではないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Not Pars after, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:48.79,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,我らの利害は　いまだ一致しているはず
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Our interests can still be aligned.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:52.81,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なるほど　そういうことか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Clear. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:58.18,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,よかろう　パルスの玉座はお主のものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:14:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Parsis throne will be yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.08,0:15:07.91,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ヒルメス　私をルシタニアの王にできるか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hermes, you can make me king Lyusitanii?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:11.18,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お望みとあらば　陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:15.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,もうこっちのは運び終えたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Demolition of everything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:23.55,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだかもったいないねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow even pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:27.06,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,残念ながら　ここに残していける兵力はない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, we do not have the strength to leave the people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If the bandits make their empty castle lair,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.77,0:15:32.04,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,空いた城を盗賊が根城にしては　後々困ることになるのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,later it will result in a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:39.13,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ　ルシタニアの人たちはどうなるの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what would happen to lyusitaniantsami?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.99,0:15:41.44,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか放り出したり…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not throw the same to their own devices?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.66,0:15:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Our supplies are limited, and the issue of an alarm ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.70,0:15:47.12,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,食料も限られているゆえ　悩ましい問題ではあるが…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the Prince had already decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:51.93,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,すでに殿下はお決めになっているようだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:13.39,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫か
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.69,0:16:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:15.23,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You do not need thanks. Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:17.84,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,礼などいらぬ　安静にな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.57,0:16:20.63,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いってぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Painfully!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:23.41,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,おっと　落ち着け　ゆっくりやるから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Quietly. I'll be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:24.75,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あ痛ててて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Months and months and months!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:27.33,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,動くな　また傷口が開くぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.05,0:16:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And the wounds open again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:29.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,じっとしていろ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.78,0:16:33.33,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,男なら辛抱しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a man, be patient!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.77,0:16:33.32,UP JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いっ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:38.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だ　私が必ず皆を故郷に送り届けてやるからな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I'll take you to our country.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.69,0:16:40.39,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,よし
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.13,0:16:44.52,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,不器用なヤツ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're incompetent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Only you know how to handle a sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:47.28,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に剣しか扱えないんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:48.87,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだと
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.87,0:16:50.87,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,貸せ　教えてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.99,0:16:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I will teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:56.65,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,{\fs53}自分から負傷者たちの世話をさせろって　殿下に頼んでついてきたんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You do require to take care of the wounded,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and I asked the Prince to agree, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:17:00.46,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,だったら　足手まといになるなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:17:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then do not be a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:02.01,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,よし
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:13.25,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫か　疲れただろう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? Tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:15.88,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,平気よ　これくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:18.10,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,今　水をくんでくる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:23.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あの娘　少し変わっているな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.11,0:17:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl is a little different.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:25.43,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,娘なのか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:27.69,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なかなか健気ではないか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.16,0:17:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite gallant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.75,0:17:29.49,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:36.75,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,精が出るな　ルシタニアの少女よ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.95,0:17:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all the work, a girl from Lyusitanii.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.54,0:17:39.15,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あまり女扱いするな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.65,0:17:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not treat me like a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:42.44,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,慣れぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:49.46,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お主は進んであいつに仕えていると言ったな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.22,0:17:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that you serve it on their own, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.70,0:17:50.23,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,うむ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:55.57,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ皆　あのような青二才の王太子に忠実に仕えておるのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so faithfully serve such an inexperienced Crown Prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.81,0:17:59.62,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,玉座にはそれ自身の意思はない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In the throne there own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.68,0:18:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.73,0:18:03.54,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私はこう考えている
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.42,0:18:05.56,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,座る者によって
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Depending on who is sitting on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:09.73,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それは正義の椅子にもなるし　悪逆の席にもなる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.34,0:18:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,he may become the seat of justice or cruelty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:15.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,神ならぬ人間が政を行う以上　完璧であることもないが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,While driving is not a god, but a man,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.27,0:18:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,he can not be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.31,0:18:19.04,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それに近づこうとする努力を怠れば
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But he should not hanker to attain perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.67,0:18:24.88,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,誰も止める者がいないままに　王は悪への坂を転げ落ちるであろう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If anyone will not be around,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,King will come to the path of evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:30.91,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,王太子殿下はいつも努力しておられる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.85,0:18:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Crown Prince always endeavors.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.87,0:18:35.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そのことが仕える者の目には明らかなだけなのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This fact is obvious to all who serve him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:39.51,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,掛けがえのないお方と思うゆえに
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We see how people will relate to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:42.03,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,皆喜んで仕えておるのじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and happy to serve him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:44.12,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お主はどうじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.30,0:18:48.13,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私はお前たちの動きを見張っているだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just following your movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:49.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,せいぜい気をつけろ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:52.40,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,何あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.61,0:18:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.87,0:18:54.50,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,憎ったらしい子だねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.92,0:18:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Nasty girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:58.75,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そうもパルスが嫌いなら　ついてくることなんかないのにさ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.08,0:18:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If she hates Parsa so I did not go to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:08.07,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,もう出来るぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:14.41,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様　なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You! What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:17.06,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,この経典を君に返そうと思って
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.86,0:19:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you back this book.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:21.27,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,来い
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.64,0:19:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.27,0:19:22.75,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,痛てて…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Months and months and months!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.61,0:19:26.70,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,王太子のくせに不用心だぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.71,0:19:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a prince! And so recklessly behaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:29.53,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか　いつもこんな感じだが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.87,0:19:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? I always conduct myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:31.42,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,何なんだ　この軍は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with this army ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.55,0:19:34.03,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,大切なものをありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for an important book.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:39.69,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,返す必要はない　私がお前を改宗させてやるのだから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.36,0:19:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You can not return.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make you accept our faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.92,0:19:41.69,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それはないと思うが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:43.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,用事はそれだけか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.33,0:19:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You came just for that ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.99,0:19:46.31,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ…　手伝えることはあるか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.15,0:19:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I help with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:50.19,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,王位継承者だというなら　もっと偉そうにしていろ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you're the future ruler! Behave more arrogantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:08.31,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,おお　元気な男の子じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.66,0:20:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What is a healthy boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:16.42,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,エトワール様
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady of the Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Somewhere hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:18.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ　どこか痛いか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:20.88,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,抱いてあげて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.33,0:20:22.67,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,わ…私が
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I can not look at it! Child like this keep!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:32.69,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,見ちゃいられないね　赤ん坊はこう抱くんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:35.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,よしよし　もう大丈夫だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.09,0:20:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet, quiet. All is well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.34,0:20:36.02,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:37.37,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,To her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:41.91,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いい子だねぇ　きっと立派な盗賊になるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Good boy! Become a great bandit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.95,0:20:45.24,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,とんでもない　この子はルシタニアの騎士になるのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.02,0:20:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I do not! He becomes a knight Lyusitanii!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.03,0:21:01.40,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,どのような神を信じるのであれ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.08,0:21:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In whatever gods they may believe
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.06,0:21:06.36,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,人々の慈しみがこの子の道を照らしますように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.14,0:21:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,may love and compassion will pave the way to the bright child.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.91,0:21:33.49,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,随分と長い旅をしてきた感じがする
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems as if we have done a terribly long way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:37.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ　あの日　二人で始めた戦でした
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.94,0:21:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. For us, it all started with the war in the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.55,0:21:41.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューンよ　思い出に浸るにはまだ随分と早い
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.66,0:21:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Daryun, it is too early to reminisce.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:43.65,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,気を抜く暇はないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.39,0:21:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not lose vigilance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.12,0:21:48.15,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,バカを言え　俺の体は常に気合いでみなぎっている
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.13,0:21:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not Bring nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.75,0:21:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My body is always full of fighting spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.62,0:21:53.15,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下　やはりこやつには戦うこと以外ないようですな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.71,0:21:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.86,0:21:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like he has no other qualities, but to a great warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.62,0:21:54.53,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.78,0:21:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.22,0:21:59.53,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そういうお前こそ　戦で策を巡らす以外　何もできないではないか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.42,0:21:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And you? Besides inventing different military strategies
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.27,0:21:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing else do not know how!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.98,0:22:03.13,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私は生まれついての芸術家なのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.03,0:22:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I drew you to the right path!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.17,0:22:04.58,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あれのどこがだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.27,0:22:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you drawing ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.11,0:22:08.93,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,耳ある者よ　聞けよかし
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.15,0:22:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have ears, listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.57,0:22:14.01,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,美き国パルスの物語を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.58,0:22:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the tale of the beautiful kingdom of Parsa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.54,0:22:18.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,心ある者よ　思いおこし
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.61,0:22:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You, with a pure heart, remember the rule liberator Arslan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:22.40,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,解放王アルスラーンの御代を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.38,0:22:29.62,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,見つけてやろうか　殿下のために
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.48,0:22:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether to go on a quest?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.41,0:22:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince ...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.61,0:22:33.38,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,王位継承の証しとやらを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.70,0:22:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And prove that he is worthy of the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.79,0:22:38.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,行くぞ　エクバターナ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.87,0:22:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! In Ecbatana!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.32,0:22:43.57,END JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur1\fad(150,150)}風がざわめき　砕けた気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.21,0:22:44.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,パルス暦３２１年５月
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.26,0:22:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The era of Parsis, May 321 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.62,0:22:48.73,END JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur1\fad(150,150)}見透かしてるようで震えたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.52,0:22:48.59,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,王太子アルスラーン　時に１５歳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.63,0:22:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Crown Prince Arslan 15 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.21,0:22:53.52,END JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur1\fad(150,150)}満ちた月の日　遠吠えの命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.51,0:22:52.43,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,少年は　そして王となる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the guy would be King.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.58,0:22:58.30,END JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur1\fad(150,150)}「まだ置いていかないでよ！」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.33,0:23:08.08,END JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}僕ら取り返せるかな　色つきの空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.17,0:23:17.86,END JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}埃まみれの夢舞い上げて　拳を握ったなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.04,0:23:23.57,END JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}いま走れ　走れ　旋風になって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.64,0:23:27.97,END JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}劣等　絶望　一切吹き飛ばしていく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.02,0:23:32.97,END JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}追いかけなきゃ　最後の扉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.04,0:23:36.15,END JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}何度散ったって　大逆転
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.20,0:23:42.93,END JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}この声が嗄れたって　祈りの歌届けたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.97,0:23:50.80,END JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}足りない僕らで信じてた世界を奪うまで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.91,0:23:55.37,END JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}まだまだ　まだまだ　負けられない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:24:03.57,END JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,550)}僕らは渦の中　まだまだまだ　くたばれない
